data.description:
This home features updated electric and plumbing and newer hvac. There is vinyl flooring
throughout the main level. The kitchen has been remodeled and includes stainless
appliances and an island. Both bathrooms have been remodeled and there is a large front
and back porch. The upper level has fresh carpet the second bathroom, three bedrooms and
the character of a 1920's home.
